    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous about maintenance and kept it tucked away in the garage, so it\u2019s basically flawless. You won't find a single scratch on it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and is ready for some new adventures, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
