    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 718 Cayman S, featuring a mid-mounted 2.5L turbocharged flat-four equipped with Variable Turbine Geometry (VTG) for an exceptionally linear power band and instantaneous boost response. This example is mated to a lightning-fast PDK dual-clutch transaxle and features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), ensuring optimal damping and roll stiffness. The vehicle exhibits factory-spec tolerances, flawless paint depth, and a pristine undercarriage. Meticulously maintained with a comprehensive service dossier, this chassis offers unparalleled torsional rigidity and peak mechanical performance for the discerning purist.",
