    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free from swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every body panel aligns perfectly, reflecting its documented accident-free history. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the precision navigation, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is peerless, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio and a lifetime of preventative maintenance. It drives with the same tightness and responsiveness as it did the day it left the dealership. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning enthusiast to own a definitive, investment-grade example.",
      "price": 48500.0,
