      "description": "Hey there! You've absolutely gotta see this beauty! I\u2019m parting with my pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014it practically looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve been so meticulous with its care, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for that 'brand new' experience without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you! I'd love for it to go to a great home, so feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
